chobngam My name is Nu-i Chobngam. My nickname is ice. I live with my parents. I'm in 2nd year at Prince of songkla university. :book: My birth date is 8 Jan 1995. :cake: Now I'm 20 years old. :girl: My hobbies is listen to music :musical_note: and read the book. My hobby is drawing pictures. My favorite sport is badminton.
